      "text": "To have a diagram here:\nDiagram\nOne exclidraw should \ncontain many information, like the\nprogress, the design of the model,\netc.\nMaybe for each task, we should have\na exclidraw diagram to record the\nprogress. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "To have a diagram here:\nDiagram\nOne exclidraw should \ncontain many information, like the progress, the design of the model, etc.\nMaybe for each task, we should have a exclidraw diagram to record the progress. ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
